lead_paragraph: Michael Phelps captured his 23rd and final Olympic gold medal on Saturday as the United States sealed a week of dominance in the pool by winning the men's and women's medley relays.

headline.main: Swimming: Phelps Wins Last Relay Gold as U.S. Dominate
